sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: New Firewall Rule Added Via Netsh.EXE
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the addition of a new rule to the Windows firewall via netsh

match_context.values: @{CommandLine="%windir%\System32\netsh.exe" advfirewall firewall add rule name="Host-process for services of Windows" dir=in action=allow program="%windir%\SysWOW64\svchost.exe" enable=yes>nul; Image=%windir%\System32\netsh.exe; EventID=1}

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the creation of a new service using the "sc.exe" utility.

match_context.values: @{CommandLine="%windir%\System32\sc.exe" create nbekkvkj binPath= "%windir%\SysWOW64\nbekkvkj\bnzebhgu.exe /d\"%SAMPLEPATH%\"" type= own start= auto DisplayName= "wifi support"; Image=%windir%\System32\sc.exe; EventID=1}
